---
// Community section: field notes shared on Reddit
// Anchor: community | Three posts about token economics, orchestration, security
// No props
---

<section class="community-section">
  <p class="section-moral">
    <em>The shepherd posted his flock's numbers; the wolves already knew theirs.</em>
  </p>

  <h2 id="community">Community — field notes in public</h2>

  <p class="community-intro">
    Writes on Reddit as <a href="https://reddit.com/user/rehtorical" class="reddit-link">u/rehtorical</a>.
    <span class="community-theme">token economics · agent orchestration · AI security</span>
  </p>

  <!-- Featured post -->
  <div class="featured-post">
    <div class="featured-badge">FEATURED</div>
    <article class="reddit-post">
      <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ClaudeAI/comments/1uuib78/" class="post-link">
        <h3>A single AI agent session hit 534,000 tokens in one turn (2.7x the usual 200K ceiling)</h3>
      </a>
      <p class="post-meta">r/ClaudeAI · field data from a 1,320-turn orchestration session</p>
      <p class="post-desc">Publishing live metrics from the fleet itself — how far can a single agent push the token ceiling before coherence breaks.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <!-- Additional posts -->
  <ul class="post-list">
    <li>
      <article class="reddit-post">
        <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ClaudeAI/comments/" class="post-link">
          <h3>MFA rotation can't stop modern attacks</h3>
        </a>
        <p class="post-meta">r/ClaudeAI · 19 upvotes</p>
        <p class="post-desc">Consent phishing hands attackers authorized tokens that survive credential resets. OAuth-chaining vulnerabilities become flawlessly executable by agents. Hardware keys (YubiKey) remain the practical defense.</p>
      </article>
    </li>
    <li>
      <article class="reddit-post">
        <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/vibecoding/" class="post-link">
          <h3>Simple Claude structure to save tokens</h3>
        </a>
        <p class="post-meta">r/vibecoding</p>
        <p class="post-desc">Practical token-economics structure for Claude sessions. Discipline beats cleverness.</p>
      </article>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<style>
  .community-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-20);
  }

  /* Use shared .section-moral and section h2 from global.css */

  .community-intro {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .reddit-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reddit-link {
      transition: none;
    }
  }

  .reddit-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-light);
  }

  .reddit-link:focus-visible {
    outline: var(--focus-ring);
    outline-offset: var(--focus-ring-offset);
    border-radius: 0.125rem;
  }

  .community-theme {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  /* Featured post section */
  .featured-post {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .reddit-post {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background-color var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out),
                border-color var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reddit-post {
      transition: none;
    }
  }

  .reddit-post:hover {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .post-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .post-link:focus-visible {
    outline: var(--focus-ring);
    outline-offset: var(--focus-ring-offset);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }

  .reddit-post h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .post-meta {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
  }

  .post-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  /* Post list */
  .post-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .post-list li {
    display: flex;
  }

  .post-list .reddit-post {
    width: 100%;
  }
</style>
